This is a rewrite of Thibaut Despoulain's HexGL game using TypeScript and Filament.
I tilt my hat to Thibaut and everyone who contributed to his project.
ğŸ©ğŸ

To build the web app, clone the repo twice: once for master and once for gh-pages.

    git clone https://github.com/prideout/hexgl.git hexgl_source
    git clone -b gh-pages https://github.com/prideout/hexgl.git hexgl_public
    cd hexgl_source
    yarn install
    yarn build
    cd ../hexgl_public
    npx http-server
